1. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper focuses on identifying users of handheld devices, which is a common topic in the field of HCI. 
2. cs.BIO (Computational Biology) - The paper proposes a new biometric measure based on human tremor, which falls under the scope of computational biology. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper uses smartphone built-in inertial sensors to measure hand tremor, which can be considered as a form of computer vision. 
4. cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) - The paper proposes a new method for user identification, which is a common topic in cybersecurity. 
5. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper presents a new method for identifying users of handheld devices, which can be considered as a software engineering problem.
